CatDescriptText: Post 913 club was located on the corner of Frankstown Avenue and Braddock Avenue in Homewood Bruston.
TitMainTitle: Twelve men wearing military uniforms, standing behind group of tables pushed together with tablecloth, including man with hands on tabletop podium inscribed "Commander Sportsmen's Post 913" and seal inscribed "US American Legion" with "US American Legion Sportsmen's Post 913" painted on wall, in Post 913 in Homewood Brushton.
